snippet.title: Rajasthan New CM: संगठन में भरोसेमंद- ब्राह्मण चेहरा, Bhajanlal कैसे बने मुख्यमंत्री? 4 फैक्टर
snippet.description:
Bhajan Lal Sharma Next Rajasthan CM: 56 साल का शख्त BJP के टिकट पर पहली बार चुनाव लड़ता है. उसे उस सीट से खड़ा किया जाता है जो बीजेपी की सुरक्षित सीटों में से एक हैं. इसके लिए वसुंधरा राजे के करीबी का टिकट भी काट दिया जाता है. नतीजे आते हैं और वो शख्स चुनाव जीतकर विधायक बन जाता है. लेकिन इस कहानी का क्लाइमेक्स सभी को चौंकाने वाला है. पहली बार विधायक बना ये शख्स वसुंधरा राजे को साइड कर सीधे मुख्यमंत्री बन जाता है. नाम भजनलाल शर्मा (Bhajan Lal Sharma, Next Rajasthan CM). 12 दिसंबर की तारीख. जयपुर में विधायक दल की बैठक में वसुंधरा के हाथ में एक पर्ची दिखती है. बगल में राजनाथ सिंह बैठे हुए हैं. पर्ची खुलती है और मोदी मैजिक होता है. चौंकाने वाला मैजिक. भजनलाल शर्मा को मुख्यमंत्री घोषित किया जाता है. ऐसे में सवाल उठता है कि जो रेस में दिख ही नहीं रहा था वह अचानक विनर कैसे बन गया? इसे 4 फैक्टर के जरिए समझते हैं.

#bhajanlalsharma  #rajasthannewcm  #rajasthan #vasundhararaje  #rajasthanelection2023 #bjp 

56 year old Shakht is contesting elections for the first time on BJP ticket. He is fielded from a seat which is one of the safe seats of BJP. For this, the ticket of someone close to Vasundhara Raje is also canceled. The results come and that person wins the election and becomes an MLA. But the climax of this story is shocking everyone. This person, who became MLA for the first time, leaves Vasundhara Raje aside and directly becomes the Chief Minister. Name Bhajan Lal Sharma (Bhajan Lal Sharma, Next Rajasthan CM). Date of 12th December. A slip is seen in Vasundhara's hand at the legislative party meeting in Jaipur. Rajnath Singh is sitting next to him. The slip opens and Modi magic happens. Shocking magic. Bhajanlal Sharma is declared the Chief Minister. In such a situation, the question arises that how did someone who was not visible in the race suddenly become the winner? Let us understand this through 4 factors.

क्विंट हिंदी की स्वतंत्र पत्रकारिता का साथ दीजिए. हमारे मेंबर बनिए: https://bit.ly/3jD4lfe

snippet.title: Clash of Clans Town Hall 16 Dev Update!
snippet.description:
The Town Hall 16 update is here! Join Community Manager, Ferri, as he shares what you can expect in this update! New Hero Equipment, merged buildings, Root Rider, Spirit Fox, and more are ready for you to take into battle in the biggest update of 2023! Clash on!

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

snippet.title: किस बात से भड़क रहे है Jethalal? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 11 Dec 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Bhide discusses the problem regarding the flat with Chanda Ramani, who decides that in such a situation there is only one way out, an auction. He decides to hold an auction for his flat, and the highest bidder will get the flat so there are no more problems for Bhide. 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 479
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Dune: Part Two | Official Trailer 3
snippet.description:
You are not prepared for what is to come. #DunePartTwo - Only in theaters March 1.

The saga continues as award-winning filmmaker Denis Villeneuve embarks on “Dune: Part Two,” the next chapter of Frank Herbert’s celebrated novel Dune, with an expanded all-star international ensemble cast. The film, from Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures, is the highly anticipated follow-up to 2021’s six-time Academy Award-winning “Dune.”

The big-screen epic continues the adaptation of Frank Herbert’s acclaimed bestseller Dune with returning and new stars, including Oscar nominee Timothée Chalamet (“Wonka,” “Call Me by Your Name”), Zendaya (“Spider-Man: No Way Home,” “Malcolm & Marie,” “Euphoria”), Rebecca Ferguson (“Mission: Impossible – Dead Reckoning”), Oscar nominee Josh Brolin (“Avengers: End Game,” “Milk”), Oscar nominee Austin Butler (“Elvis,” “Once Upon A Time…In Hollywood”), Oscar nominee Florence Pugh (“Black Widow,” “Little Women”), Dave Bautista (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “Thor: Love and Thunder”), Oscar winner Christopher Walken (“The Deer Hunter,” “Hairspray”), Léa Seydoux (the “James Bond” franchise and “Crimes of the Future”), Souheila Yacoub (“The Braves,” “Climax”), with Stellan Skarsgård (the “Mamma Mia!” films, “Avengers: Age of Ultron”), with Oscar nominee Charlotte Rampling (“45 Years,” “Assassin’s Creed”), and Oscar winner Javier Bardem (“No Country for Old Men,” “Being the Ricardos”).

“Dune: Part Two” will explore the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a path of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, he endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.

Villeneuve directed from a screenplay he co-wrote with Jon Spaihts based on Herbert’s novel. The film is produced by Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Villeneuve, Tanya Lapointe and Patrick McCormick. The executive producers are Joshua Grode, Herbert W. Gains, Jon Spaihts, Thomas Tull, Brian Herbert, Byron Merritt, Kim Herbert, with Kevin J. Anderson serving as creative consultant.

Villeneuve is again collaborating with his “Dune” creatives: Oscar-winning director of photography Greig Fraser; Oscar-winning production designer Patrice Vermette; Oscar-winning editor Joe Walker; Oscar-winning visual effects supervisor Paul Lambert; Oscar-nominated costume designer Jacqueline West. Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer is again on hand to create the score.

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Denis Villeneuve, “Dune: Part Two.” The film is slated for a March 1, 2024 release in theaters and IMAX nationwide and internationally beginning on 28 February 2024, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: കൂടെയുള്ളവരുടെ FAKE FACES ഞെട്ടിപ്പിച്ചു! | @SimplySillyThings | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #simplysillythings #motivation 

പഠിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് വളരൂ ജോഷ് Talks-ലൂടെ- നിങ്ങളുടെ Communication Skills മെച്ചപ്പെടുത്താൻ, ജോഷ് ടോക്സിന്റെ Malayalam to English app-ൽ ചേരുക: https://bit.ly/JoshTalksMalayalamToEnglish

കൂടപ്പിറപ്പിന്റെ മരണശേഷം, ഒരുപാട് FAKE FACES തിരിച്ചറിഞ്ഞ ആളാണ് ആര്യ. തന്റെ YOUTUBE CHANNEL ആയ @SimplySillyThings -ൽ പോലും  സഹായി ആയിരുന്നു ഈ കൂടപ്പിറപ്പ്. Engineer ആയിരുന്ന ആര്യ, എങ്ങനെ YouTube-ലൂടെ വരുമാനം കണ്ടെത്തി #financiallyindependent ആയതെന്നും, #comedy sketches ചെയ്യാറുള്ള താൻ,  ജീവിതത്തിലെ പ്രയാസഘട്ടം മറികിടന്നതെങ്ങനെ എന്നും ഇന്നത്തെ ടോൾകിലൂടെ പങ്കുവെയ്ക്കുന്നു.  

In Today's Talk, we have the talented and inspiring Arya sharing her story. Arya is a popular Malayalam YouTuber, known for her engaging and informative content. However, her journey to success was not without its challenges.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com- ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com, if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayali's by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ, അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ചെറുതായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ  നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.
#contentcreator #aryareels #malayalammotivation

snippet.title: ഇനി ഇങ്ങനെയുള്ള ഉസ്താദുമാരെ കണ്ടാൽ വെറുതെ വിടരുത് എല്ലാവർക്കും ഒരു പാഠമാവട്ടെ.
snippet.description:
#quran
#motivation
#song
#baseworld
#malappuram
#malayalam
#വേങ്ങര

 മലപ്പുറം ജില്ലയിലെ വേങ്ങരയിൽ ഒരു ഉസ്താദ് ചെയ്യുന്ന ഒരു ജനസേവനമാണ് നമ്മൾ ഈ വീഡിയോയിൽ കണ്ടിട്ടുള്ളത് ആക്രിക്കടകളിൽ നിന്നും ശേഖരിച്ച് അത് കഴിയുന്ന രീതിയിൽ നന്നാക്കി എടുത്ത്  മറ്റുള്ളവർക്ക് ഉപയോഗിക്കാൻ കൊടുക്കുക എന്ന മഹാലക്ഷമാണ് അദ്ദേഹത്തിന്റെ മനസ്സിൽ ഈ ഒരു നന്മ ആരും കാണാതെ പോകരുത് നമ്മൾ വീട്ടിൽ പഴയ ഖുർആൻ സൂക്ഷിക്കാൻ മടിച്ച് എല്ലാവരും അത് പുറത്തേക്ക് തട്ടുന്നു. അത് പല രീതിയിലും പടക്കങ്ങളായും മെഴുകുതിരി ആയി തിരിച്ചു നമ്മുടെ അടുത്തേക്ക് തന്നെ വരുന്നു. വീഡിയോ ഇഷ്ടമായാൽ ഷെയർ ചെയ്യാനും അഭിപ്രായം കമന്റ് ചെയ്യാനും ലൈക് ചെയ്യാനും മറക്കല്ലേ.

snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook ginger chicken recipe by using 500 chicken legs and a huge amount of ginger. We first cut and fried the ginger separately. Then, we marinate the chicken in curd and lemon juice. Finally, we cook them all together.

The taste is delicious!

snippet.title: Manjummel Boys മലയാളം ഇൻഡസ്ട്രിയുടെ സീൻ മാറ്റും || Star Jam with Sushin Shyam | Part 2 | RJ Rafi
snippet.description:
Star Jam with Sushin Shyam || Part 2 || RJ Rafi

ദീപക് ദേവുമായിട്ടുള സിനിമയിലെ മ്യൂസിക്ക്  യാത്രയുടെ തുടക്കവും, ഇൻഡിപെൻഡന്റ് മ്യൂസിക്ക് ഡയറക്ടർ ആയ ശേഷമുള്ള ജേർണിയെ കുറിച്ചും, താൻ കമ്പോസ് ചെയ്ത ജനപ്രിയ ഗാനങ്ങളുടെയും ബാൻഡ് ഗ്രൂപിന്റെയുമൊക്കെ ഓർമ്മകൾ സ്റ്റാർ ജാമിൽ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്നു സൂപ്പർ ഹിറ്റ് മ്യൂസിക്ക് ഡയറക്ടർ സുഷിൻ ശ്യാം

Produced By     : RJ Rafi
Guest Curation : Manu Satheesh
Sound                : Vineeth TN
Camera             :  Amal Dev PD 
Edit                    :  Amal Dev PD  & Shiju KD
Design               :  Vibin Raveendran 

0:00 Highlights 
1:16 Interview

Sushin Shyam (born 13 February 1992) is an Indian music composer, instrumentalist, and singer primarily associated with Malayalam cinema. He is also a founding member of the folk metal band The Down Troddence. His music contributions to notable films such as Varathan (2018) and Kumbalangi Nights (2019) have consolidated his standing in the industry. Notably, his work on Kumbalangi Nights earned him the Kerala State Film Award for Best Music Director in 2019.
Sushin embarked on his journey as an independent composer with the film Sapthamashree Thaskaraha (2014), for which he crafted the background score. His vocal debut was facilitated by the film Neelakasham Pachakadal Chuvanna Bhoomi (2013), where he lent his voice to the song "Thaazhvaram" under the direction of composer Rex Vijayan. Sushin's range of work extends beyond music, encompassing acting roles in various films. Additionally, he has performed in several songs, including "Aadharanjali" from Romancham (2022), a composition of his own.
Sushin Shyam commenced his film career at the young age of 19, with Deepak Dev serving as his mentor. Over a span of four years, he assisted Deepak Dev in programming background scores for more than forty-five Malayalam, Tamil, and Telugu movies.[citation needed] His composition skills were showcased in the 2012 short film Oru kutti chodyam, directed by Ganesh Raj. The following year, Music Director Rex Vijayan enlisted Sushin's talent for programming the background score for Neelakasham Pachakadal Chuvanna Bhoomi. Sushin also lent his voice to a song, "Thaazhvaram," for the film.
Sushin's encounter with Rex proved to be a major turning point in his career. Encouraged by Rex, Sushin composed the background score for his next film, Sapthamashree Thaskaraha, in 2014, marking his first solo venture as a composer. In addition, he also sang the track "Kayi Ethum Doorathonde" for the film. Sushin's subsequent projects included composing the background score for Lord Livingstone 7000 Kandi in 2015 and for Kismath, directed by newcomer Shanavas Bavakkutty. He also created a song, "Kissa Pathiyil," for the latter film, both of which were well received by audiences.
In 2016, Sushin Shyam composed music for the short film Vicky, directed by Manu Joseph. The following year, he contributed to the score and two songs, "Thambiraan" and "Irulu Neelum Raave," for the horror mystery film Ezra directed by Jay.K. He then worked on the background scores for Villain and The Great Father the same year.
In 2018, he was responsible for the songs and score of three films: Maradona, Lilli, and Varathan. Notably, his work on Varathan received significant attention.
Sushin continued to make his mark in 2019 with releases like Kumbalangi Nights and Virus. In 2020, he collaborated with Jackson Vijayan to co-compose the background score for Anwar Rasheed's Trance.[28] During the same year, he composed for Kappela and also created the background score for Kilometers and Kilometers, featuring Tovino Thomas.
In 2021, Sushin had several notable releases including Malik, Kurup, and Minnal Murali. The track "Raheemun Aleemun" from Malik, performed by eight-year-old Hida Chokkad from Malappuram, achieved significant popularity and virality on the internet. Both Sushin's music and Hida's rendition were met with high praise. Another song from the same film, "Theerame Theerame", also charted highly in the year's hit lists.
The crime thriller Kurup received mixed reviews, but Sushin's music and score were widely acclaimed. The soundtrack for the superhero film Minnal Murali also gained considerable popularity, with Sajin Srijith of The New Indian Express describing it as "instantly addictive" and reminiscent of "Western retro hits". All four songs Sushin composed for this film were also well received.

snippet.description:
What is Article 370 Malayalam? Jammu and Kashmir Verdict 2023 | alexplain

The government of India abrogated Article 370 of the Indian constitution in 2019 to remove the special status of Jammu and Kashmir. The move of the central government to scrap Article 370, article 35A etc to remove the special status of Jammu and Kashmir was challenged in the Supreme Court of India. In its unanimous verdict, the Supreme Court's five-judge bench upheld the abrogation of Article 370. This video explains the history behind the introduction of Article 370 and the special status of Jammu and Kashmir. The constitutional side of Article 370 and its abrogation is explained in this video.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:

Abdul is missing and Bharat suspects him to have stolen the money. He later threatens Jethalal to file a police complaint against him. Will Jethalal land into legal trouble?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 380
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Mannat Murad Episode 22 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 11th December 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

Episode - 1668-1670

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.description:
પ્રસ્તુત છે રાકેશ બારોટ નવું ગુજરાતી બેવફા ગીત "વાયરા વિયોગ ના વાયા" જુઓ ફક્ત @SaregamaGujarati પર 💜

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUzteH3czVO5WMxyPrP2RWK4MMHuCKLwL

Singer: Rakesh Barot
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Chhaya Thakor
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Director : Vishnu Thakor (Adalaj)
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Music: Ravi Nagar & Rahul Nadiya
Lyrics: Naresh Thakor (Vayad)
Co Artist: Hansamukh Meghval, Chhaya Shukla
DOP: Dhruv Bhatiya 
Editing: Ravindra S Rathod
Production: Kiratan Barot, Amar Panchal, Manthan Panchal
Makeup & Hair: Hasmukh Limbachiya, Chirag
Sport Boy: Mehul, Bittu
Light: Jitubhai, Kiran
Floor Music Arrange: Sunil Kachhiya

Lyrics:
સમય સંજોગે વાયરા વિયોગના વાયા
આજે કાળ ના ચોઘડિયા...(2)
હો લમણો ના વાળ્યો થોડો મારા હોમું
યાદ કરું બેસી ને બાવળિયે

હો મારા કિસ્મત ફૂટ્યા તમે મારાથી રૂઠ્યાં
હૈયે હેત ચમ ફૂટ્યા આંખે ઓંહુઁડા ખૂટ્યા
એ તારો અવાજ હૉમ્ભલ્વા કોલ રેકોર્ડિંગ મેં રાખ્યા
ગોડી કોઈ ના આવ્યું હમજ રે
એ તારા મારા ફોટા ફોન ના લોકર માં હંતાડ્યા
ફોટા ભમે મારી નજરે
હો લમણો ના વાળ્યો થોડો મારા હોમું
યાદ કરું બેસી ને બાવળિયે

નોને થી લઇ ગોંડી મારી હારે થયા મોટા
યાદ આવે એ દાડે મારા હલી જાય રુવાડા
કોલેજ માં મેં બર્થડે ઉજવ્યો પાડ્યા ભેળા મેં ફોટા
જોવું છું એ ફોટા મારા આંસુ ના રોકાતા

હો તારા કરેલા એ ફોન મારુ રાખતી બૌ ધ્યાન
મને પડી ના કોઈ જોણ આજે ભૂલી ગઈ ઓળખાણ
બનાસ વાળી બસમાં ભણવા ભેળા ભેળા જાતા ગોંડી ચમ કરી વિહારે
એ ગોમ ના બસ સ્ટેડ ભેળ પકોડી રે ખાતા બકા ચમ કરી વિહારે

તમે લમણો ના વાળ્યો થોડો મારા હોમું
યાદ કરું બેસી ને બાવળિયે
પ્રેમ ના એ પાઠ તમે પલભર માં વિહરાયા
મન મૉન્યા બીજા હારે દલડાં બદલાયા

કઠણ કરયા કાળજા ને પથ્થર ખડકાયા
આવું સુ પાસી કઈ ને મુખ ના બતાયા
હો મને મળવાનું ચુકી ગઈ તું અંધારા માં મૂકી
નીકળી જીવની તું ટૂંકી થઇ ગઈ મારાથી વિખુટી

હો 0156 તારા મારા પ્રેમ નો પાસવર્ડ
ચમ કરી તને આ ભુલાયો
હો લમણો ના વાળ્યો થોડો મારા હોમું
યાદ કરું બેસી ને બાવળિયે
સમય સંજોગે વાયરા વિયોગના વાયા
આજે કાળ ના ચોઘડિયા
